{"id":105123,"type":1,"name":"Dämons","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/c3/33/105123_kI7db.jpg","rating":{"total":4,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":0,"5":1,"6":1,"7":0,"8":2,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.8},"summary":"　　１年前兵斗還只是個在高科技上班的上班族，因為他與公司理念不和而被視為叛徒，竟然遭到他的５位好友聯手毀了他的雙手，甚至還用自己研發的科技把妻子跟女兒給害死了，面對這一切他陷入了瘋狂，滿腦子只剩下憤怒。後來他被人發現交給了貝克爾博士，博士經過一番拷問之後認為他有資格裝上自己研發的高科技義肢，於是他重新有了一雙鐵手臂…。\r\n　　本書敘述男人因為絕望憤怒所展開的復仇劇，而令人不可思議的就是書中所描寫的念動力〝塞斯摩斯〞…。","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>恶魔</li><li><span>册数: </span>13</li><li><span>话数: </span>116</li><li><span>作者: </span><a href=\"/person/15077\">米原秀幸</a></li><li><span>出版社: </span><a href=\"/person/7571\">秋田書店</a>、<a href=\"/person/7033\">東立出版社</a>、<a href=\"/person/8163\">天下出版</a></li><li><span>连载杂志: </span><a href=\"/person/6111\">週刊少年チャンピオン</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/1318\">手塚治虫</a></li><li><span>别名: </span>Dämons ～惡魔～</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>复仇鬼</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>復仇鬼</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Damons</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>ダイモンズ</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Dämons - 「鉄の旋律」より</li><li><span>开始: </span>2006年10号</li><li><span>结束: </span>2008年29号</li>","collection":{"wish":6,"collect":6,"on_hold":1,"dropped":1},"tags":[{"name":"米原秀幸","count":3},{"name":"CC","count":1},{"name":"漫画","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":15077,"image":"","name":"米原秀幸","desc":"作者"},{"id":7033,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/fd/24/7033_prsn_J3N83.jpg","name":"东立出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":7571,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/28/b1/7571_prsn_vckUV.jpg","name":"秋田书店","desc":"出版社"},{"id":8163,"image":"","name":"天下出版社","desc":"出版社"},{"id":6111,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/e0/03/6111_prsn_oKyko.jpg","name":"周刊少年Champion","desc":"连载杂志"},{"id":1318,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/76/cf/1318_prsn_anidb.jpg","name":"手冢治虫","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":152734,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/3f/0d/152734_jp.jpg","title"